{"tid":995133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港公主 vs 我認我港女","createTime":"2019-01-25T08:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T08:34:03.000Z","uid":51200,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a52b6d7701a33c58457299e37c95559dd28d08f","tid":995133,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"杜如風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ReuExyk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReuExyk.png&h=d27395fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於加拿大麥馬士達大學修讀城市規劃，副修日語，其後參與當地「在加國學生日本語演講比賽」獲全國冠軍，考取到日本文部省（教育局）獎學金，獲日本駐加國大使夫人賞識，推介她在大學畢業後到東京的御茶水女子大學主修日本文學，故放棄多倫多大學的碩士課程[9]。<br />\n<br />\nVs<br />\n<br />\n吳若希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aEpJFd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aEpJFd.png&h=f2604472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多新聞<br />\n唔quote 了<br />\n<br />\n大家點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a392c49f812b261835d7dc6f132f0210d7274a9e","tid":995133,"uid":214152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"梗係杜如風"},{"pid":"d02e689632345b479de2ad42f46a2cc167e36b6c","tid":995133,"uid":76314,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"香港公主就扮on 9搵食，另外個隻臭雞就真on 9，會倒自己老公米，俾你點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e201ba33c3487b9d66329ac8ede7c0b4daac71","tid":995133,"uid":31200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"杜如風高好多班喎 同個無腦既比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830c7c0bffadcf4e0c2a14b370e597fc4c69b924","tid":995133,"uid":139873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"824973efc579a325fe75eabc5f565ade8c9fa77e","tid":995133,"uid":205809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"港咩女 支那出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20010247480ab0b0a44e4d5c781d1f0338beaddd","tid":995133,"uid":149253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"文部省 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3f53a1650ae483f6bf198595d92a2dd527473d","tid":995133,"uid":189528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"824973efc579a325fe75eabc5f565ade8c9fa77e","tid":995133,"uid":205809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"港咩女 支那出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"佢想認港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08382351dc71a1d6fcc38b8f78c7069a86c94d2d","tid":995133,"uid":886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"你知道杜如風既歷史後<br />\n就明白,佢係正宗香港公主<br />\n唔係公主病,而係伸隻手出黎有人埋單<br />\n話今日好悶就會有10個男仔渣車係樓下等<br />\n放工會有仔渣車搶頭淡湯等<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都唔知佢乜來頭<br />\n就算80後都未必人人知<br />\n但知道既會覺得佢係好撚傳奇<br />\n根本係公主既教母<br />\n<br />\n如果話佢係港女<br />\n不如話佢係皇帝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但女仔始終係會老既<br />\n如果係全盛時期,真係玩撚哂<br />\n以家都唔弱<br />\n<br />\n再者港女想佢去個級數都仲有距離<br />\n因為佢想食飯就會有10個 8個男仔爭比錢<br />\n直頭唔洗同你&rdquo;港&ldquo;<br />\n人地埋單係常識,當然佢有錢自己比,自己屋企都唔係弱<br />\n<br />\n拎港女同佢比,根本就係ON9<br />\n港女臭西扮哂野要R返黎既野,係佢身上係無限咁有人比,唔洗R的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想講句,<br />\n某D巴絲們,你地太年輕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢野既人,會當佢死肥婆行出黎攪攪陣<br />\n知佢野既人,就會明白自己連追佢既條件都未有<br />\n就算係高登仔條件既,係佢眼中都只屬一般<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果自己唔識既就上去GOOGLE<br />\n就如見到巴菲特<br />\n話呢個呀叔有乜巴閉呀,咁多人圍住佢既<br />\n一樣"},{"pid":"32899548f3234173b42384eca67405398048aed2","tid":995133,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"差咁多皮,正常人都揀杜如風啦<br />\n淨係星雅廊單野已經贏唔止十條街<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 等睇回覆幾時開始有1負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}